Romaine Fielding https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romaine_Fielding 0 Romaine Fielding (born William Grant Blandin, May 22, 1867 – December 15, 1927) was an American actor, screenwriter, and silent film director known for his dramatic westerns.
